How Do You Think Technology Affects Dating?

Have you had any experience with dating? Have you ever used dating apps? If so, what has it been like for you? If not, why not?

How do you think technology — like apps, Netflix, social media and texting — affects dating and relationships? In your opinion, does it improve or worsen romantic interactions? How so?

---

In my opinion,

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I've found that dating apps in particular increase the odds of finding a relationship, at least for me.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: I think technology does a really good job in helping alleviate anxiety, but it never fully prepares you for a first impression.

actions.name: text-insert
actions.text: But overall, technology has definitely helped me in my dating experiences.
